patthana23.50:1.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ naparittaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho paritto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.50:2.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ namahaggataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho mahaggato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.50:3.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ naappamāṇaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho appamāṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
